Package: threshtvp
Title: Bayesian Estimation of (Threshold) Time-Varying Parameter Models
Version: 0.3
Authors@R: as.person(c(
    "Florian Huber <fhuber7@gmail.com> [aut, cre]", 
    "Gregor Kastner <gregor.kastner@wu.ac.at> [aut]"))
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0), stochvol, GIGrvg, MASS, dlm
Description: Inference in dynanmic regression models and threshold time-varying
    parameter vector autoregressions (TTVP-VARs) with mixture innovation
    components for each coefficient in the system.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.11.6)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
NeedsCompilation: yes
